  <name>BigTube</name>
  <summary>Universal multimedia downloader</summary>

  <description>
    <p>
      BigTube is a modern GTK4/libadwaita front-end for yt-dlp. Paste a link or
      search by keywords to download video and audio from a wide range of
      websites, pick the exact quality you want, convert media, and manage your
      downloads — all from a clean, native desktop interface.
    </p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Download video or audio in any available quality (H.264, VP9, AV1, AAC, Opus, MP3…)</li>
      <li>Side-by-side video and audio format picker, with on-the-fly conversion</li>
      <li>Built-in media converter — drag and drop files to transcode</li>
      <li>Batch downloads with concurrent fragments for speed</li>
      <li>Automatic cover art embedding for audio downloads</li>
      <li>Optional startup check that keeps yt-dlp up to date</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

  <launchable type="desktop-id">org.big.bigtube.desktop</launchable>

